  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Are you passionate about audio-visual technology and driven by sales excellence?</strong></p><p>We are seeking a <strong>Sales Manager</strong> with strong leadership capabilities to drive sales initiatives, mentor team members, and deliver tailored audio-visual solutions to our clients.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Lead, manage, and develop the sales team to achieve individual and team sales targets.</li><li>Build and maintain strong relationships with both new and existing clients.</li><li>Understand client needs and recommend appropriate audio-visual solutions.</li><li>Promote and sell the Company’s full range of audio-visual products and integrated systems.</li><li>Conduct product demonstrations, presentations, and solution briefings.</li><li>Collaborate closely with technical and project teams to ensure customer requirements are met.</li><li>Monitor sales performance, prepare forecasts, and drive continuous improvement in sales results.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Proven sales experience in the audio-visual, IT, or technology industry, with leadership or team management exposure.</li><li>Strong technical knowledge of audio-visual products, solutions, and market trends.</li><li>Excellent leadership, communication, presentation, and negotiation skills.</li><li>Results-driven, self-motivated, and able to work both independently and as part of a team.</li></ul><p><strong>We Offer</strong></p><ul><li>Competitive remuneration package with attractive bonuses.</li><li>Opportunities for career progression and leadership development in a growing organization.</li><li>A dynamic, supportive, and collaborative work environment.</li><li>Structured training and professional development programs.</li></ul>",
